Editor's Note:With the 2022 Beijing Winter Olympics drawing to a close, athletes from all over the world have expressed their appreciation and heartfelt thanks to the considerate, exquisite and trustworthy support provided by the organizers and staff. From the meticulous cuisines to reliable medical care, from effective epidemic prevention to the timely support in extreme weather conditions, China has delivered a smooth and wonderful sports event which has witnessed athletes' breakthroughs on ice and snow. 

